I served with a unit at the Danang airbase 71-72...this unit was known as FLEET AIR SUPPORT UNIT, DANANG.  I have yet to see this unit or the naval presence at Danang mentioned in any literature.<br><br>
CO at the time was &quot;Red Dog&quot; Davidson...XO was LtCmdr Raudio.<br><br>
Our mission was to patch wounded birds to send back to Yankee Station, refuel live birds, etc.<br><br>
Has anyone seen any information on this unit?  This may be one unit that drifts into the fog of time.
